#{123}{}{Uh, good.}
{123}{}{呃，很好。 -- Uh, good.}
#{130}{}{What do you want from me, young man?}
{130}{}{年轻人，你想从我这里得到什么？ -- What do you want from me, young man?}
#{131}{}{Nothing right now. Goodbye.}
{131}{}{现在什么都没有。再见。 -- Nothing right now. Goodbye.}
